---
const stackPrimary = ["React", "TypeScript", "Java", "Spring Boot", "PostgreSQL"];
const stackSecondary = ["Docker", "OAuth2", "JWT", "Redux Toolkit", "Liquibase", "CI/CD"];
---

<section class="section about-sec" id="sobre">
	<div class="sec-head lr">
		<div>
			<p class="sec-index">01 / Retrato</p>
			<h2 class="sec-title">Sobre <em>mí</em></h2>
		</div>
		<p class="sec-note">Bilbao → producción, vía Spring Boot y React.</p>
	</div>

	<div class="about-card">
		<div class="about-grid">
			<p class="about-quote" id="about-quote">
				Construyo software con la misma cabeza con la que planificaba trayectorias para un
				monoplaza autónomo: si no funciona de verdad, en pista o en producción, no vale.
			</p>
			<div class="about-side">
				<p>
					Full Stack Developer con <strong>1,5 años de experiencia</strong>, graduado en
					Ingeniería Informática por la <strong>UPV/EHU</strong>. Me apasiona construir
					productos completos y que funcionan de verdad, no demos bonitas.
				</p>
				<p>
					Formé parte de <strong>Formula Student Bizkaia</strong>, en el equipo de conducción
					autónoma: path planning con <strong>ROS2 y Python</strong> para el monoplaza,
					compitiendo en <strong>FSUK Silverstone 2024</strong>.
				</p>

				<div class="about-stack">
					<div class="stack-group">
						<span class="stack-label">Stack principal</span>
						<div class="tags">
							{stackPrimary.map((t) => <span>{t}</span>)}
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="stack-group">
						<span class="stack-label">Y también</span>
						<div class="tags">
							{stackSecondary.map((t) => <span>{t}</span>)}
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="about-stats">
					<div class="about-stat">
						<div class="v" data-count="1.5">0</div>
						<div class="l">años exp.</div>
					</div>
					<div class="about-stat">
						<div class="v" data-count="2024">0</div>
						<div class="l">FSUK Silverstone</div>
					</div>
					<div class="about-stat">
						<div class="v">ROS2</div>
						<div class="l">path planning</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.about-card {
		background: hsl(var(--theme-text));
		color: hsl(var(--theme-bg));
		border-radius: 28px;
		padding: 4rem 3.5rem;
	}
	.about-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 0.8fr;
		gap: 4rem;
		align-items: start;
	}
	.about-quote {
		font-family: var(--font-serif);
		font-weight: 300;
		font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3.4vw, 2.7rem);
		line-height: 1.32;
		letter-spacing: -0.015em;
		margin: 0;
	}
	.about-quote :global(.w) {
		opacity: 0.18;
		transition: opacity 0.4s ease;
	}
	.about-quote :global(.w.lit) {
		opacity: 1;
	}
	.about-quote :global(em) {
		font-style: italic;
		color: var(--klein);
	}
	.about-side p {
		color: hsl(var(--theme-bg) / 0.7);
		margin: 0 0 1.4rem;
		font-size: 0.98rem;
		line-height: 1.65;
	}
	.about-side strong {
		color: hsl(var(--theme-bg));
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	.about-stack {
		margin-top: 1.8rem;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 1.1rem;
	}
	.stack-label {
		display: block;
		font-family: var(--font-mono);
		font-size: 0.68rem;
		letter-spacing: 0.1em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		color: hsl(var(--theme-bg) / 0.5);
		margin-bottom: 0.55rem;
	}
	.tags {
		display: flex;
		gap: 0.5rem;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
	}
	.tags span {
		font-family: var(--font-mono);
		font-size: 0.7rem;
		letter-spacing: 0.03em;
		border: 1px solid hsl(var(--theme-bg) / 0.2);
		border-radius: 99px;
		padding: 0.32rem 0.8rem;
		color: hsl(var(--theme-bg) / 0.85);
		transition: all 0.3s;
	}
	.about-card:hover .tags span {
		border-color: var(--klein);
	}

	.about-stats {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
		gap: 1px;
		background: hsl(var(--theme-bg) / 0.18);
		border: 1px solid hsl(var(--theme-bg) / 0.18);
		border-radius: 14px;
		overflow: hidden;
		margin-top: 2.2rem;
	}
	.about-stat {
		background: hsl(var(--theme-text));
		padding: 1.3rem 0.9rem;
		text-align: center;
	}
	.about-stat .v {
		font-family: var(--font-serif);
		font-size: 1.7rem;
		font-weight: 400;
		color: var(--klein);
		white-space: nowrap;
	}
	.about-stat .l {
		font-family: var(--font-mono);
		font-size: 0.6rem;
		letter-spacing: 0.08em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		color: hsl(var(--theme-bg) / 0.5);
		margin-top: 0.3rem;
	}

	@media (max-width: 960px) {
		.about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
		.about-card { padding: 3rem 1.8rem; }
	}
	@media (max-width: 760px) {
		.about-card { border-radius: 20px; padding: 2.6rem 1.4rem; }
	}
	@media (max-width: 480px) {
		.about-stats { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
	}
</style>
